msgid "State Data Hierarchy"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: ./modules/salt/pages/salt-config-management.adoc:16
msgid ""
"State data comes from {productname} in the form of package and custom states "
"and targets clients at three specific levels of hierarchy.  The state "
"hierarchy is defined by the following order or priority: individual clients "
"have priority on packages and custom states over groups; next a group has "
"priority over the organization."
msgstr ""

